graph LR
  actor Student as A
  actor Teacher as B

  A -->|Browses| UC1(预约教师会面)
  B -->|Receives| UC1
  UC1 -->|Sends Request| B
  UC1 -->|Receives Response| A
  UC1 -.->|Accepts Request| A: Confirm Notification
  UC1 -.->|Rejects Request| A: Reject Notification
  UC1 -.->|No Suitable Time| A: Reselect Teacher
  UC1 -.->|No Response in Time| A: System Cancels Request
